Localization.Name: Asgard 2955 Ship Showdown Poster
Localization.Description: Featuring a massive ramp designed to accommodate large ground vehicles and the rapid deployment of troops and supplies, it's no surprise the Anvil Asgard found itself in the final four of the 2955 Ship Showdown. This poster honors the accomplishment with an image of the ship streaking across colorful, cloud-filled sky.
